keyMappings:
unmap gs
unmap p
unmap x
unmap T
unmap W
unmap X
unmap <<
unmap >>
map gb Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
map gs Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
map g[ previousTab
map g] nextTab
map g{ moveTabLeft
map g} moveTabRight
map gC removeTab
searchEngines:
nx: https://search.nixos.org/packages?channel=unstable&query=%s Nixpkgs
